<div id="msg" style="position: fixed;top: 200px;left: 270px;width:1300px;height:600px;background-color:#f0f0f0;display:none;opacity: 0.7;">
<br /><br /><br /><p align=center><font face=tahoma size=6 color=green><strong>ΠΑΡΑΚΑΛΩ ΠΕΡΙΜΕΝΕΤΕ</strong></font>
<br /><br />
<img src="l.gif" />
</p>
</div>
 

<script>

function p(i){
	document.getElementById("msg").style.display="block";
	document.getElementById("s").value=document.getElementById("pp"+i).innerHTML;
	document.frm.submit();
}

function e(i){
	document.getElementById("msg").style.display="block";
	document.getElementById("s").value=document.getElementById("ee"+i).innerHTML;
	document.frm.submit();
}

function dets(i){

	
	var xmlhttp=false

	if (window.XMLHttpRequest)
		{
			xmlhttp=new XMLHttpRequest();
			
		}
	else if (window.ActiveXObject)
		{
			xmlhttp = new ActiveXObject("Microsoft.XMLHTTP");
		}


	if (xmlhttp)
		{
			var DataToSend ="i="+i;

			xmlhttp.open("POST","details.asp?i="+i,false);
			xmlhttp.setRequestHeader("Content-Type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded");
			xmlhttp.send(DataToSend);

			document.getElementById("d"+i).innerHTML=xmlhttp.responseText;

			
			//document.getElementById('msg').style.display='none';

			
		}



}

</script>

</body>
</html>
